    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. This speedy sir-fry is inspired by the classic chicken and sweetcorn soup. For your version, you'll sizzle chicken, sweetcorn and spinach with garlic and chilli. Toss in basmati rice and coat the lot in a sweet-savoury soy and sesame sauce. Delicious. Under 600 calories.",
